==English==
===Noun===
#The [[pin]] or [[spindle]] on which a wheel [[revolve]]s, or which revolves with a wheel.
#A [[transverse]] bar or shaft connecting the opposite wheels of a car or carriage; an [[axletree]].
#An [[axis]]; as, the sun's axle.
